#summary This page should be a reference to the settings found on the Options tab.

*Power Bot Config:*

  # Enable window drag (move window by dragging top bar with mouse).
    Does what it says. Allows the user to drag the window by click and drag on the green top bar.
  # Remember window open state on refresh
    With this option checked, if you leave the bot dialog open and refresh the page, the bot dialog will open again when the page loads.

*KofC Features:*

  # Disable all Fairie popup windows
    Prevents the _A Traveling Faire is passing_ and _Visit court_ from opening and interrupting your gameplay.
  # Wide screen (all domains, requires refresh)
    This option removes the ads-bar from the right of the game and left aligns the game.
  # Refresh if KOC not loaded within 1 minute (all domains)
    If for some reason the page does not load within the minute a page refresh will be initiated.
  # Refresh KOC every XX minutes
    Simpy refreshes the the page at the desired interval.
  # Put chat on right (requires wide screen)
    Moves the chat-frame to the right if the game-frame and extends the chat-frame. Very nice on widescreen monitors and makes it easy to see the chat whilst working with open dialogs in the game-frame.
  # Use !WideMap (requires wide screen)
    This option extends the map-view by 5 squares to the right.
  # Auto collect gold when happiness reaches XX %
    Does the same thing that the _Increase Gold_ button in the castle dialog does, but automatically when the desired  happiness rate is reached.
 
*Extra Features:*
 # Help alliance build/research posts
  This option will post the "Post to wall" message automatically 
 # Hide alliance requests in chat
  This option automatically hides all help messages so the alliance chat is less cluttered with building spam.
 # Auto publish Facebook posts for >Everyone>Friends only>Me Only> (For all domains)
  This option publish post automatically and if check-marked it affects all your domains  
 # Show Player & Might in map.
  Alters the map to show the owners of player owned property.
